        <Parent_String>hinges by visibility [300048919], hinges (hardware) [300033367], hinges and hinge components [300246366], finish hardware (hardware) [300045309], hardware by form [300145797], hardware (components) [300033260], components by general context [300241581], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
